   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can edit the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Qualification and Benefits</b> page when the program is in <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">In Amendment</b> status.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can perform one or more of the actions listed below:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Duplicating a section</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Deleting a section</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Adding a new section</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Deleting a row</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Adding new products (qualification as well as benefits)</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Excluding a product from a product category</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Removing/Deleting exclusions</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Modifying the expression and the min/max option</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Importing product rows</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Following actions are restricted on the qualification and benefits page while amending the program.</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Editing number of tiers</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Editing the start and end date on existing product rows</li>
      </ul>
